      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-34vm1 for review-zfs-part-2 received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/66c3623d-e4e7-4347-a8c9-51b8ffb1dcfe). Ran 10 tests. No failures.",
