        ]
      },
      "date": "2017-11-09 23:20:54.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-33vm1 for review-dne-part-2 received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/a74a81d1-78cb-4061-8a90-6adcd02c5616). Ran 16 tests. No failures.",
