        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2017-11-09 23:30:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nShould this remove OBD_CONNECT_IBITS from CLIENT_CONNECT_MDT_REQD, so that in the future clients do not need to send OBD_CONNECT_IBITS at all?",
